&ldquo;Space is Hard&rdquo;
If you have ever heard an interview about space you probably heard the phrase SPACE IS HARD&hellip;
We need to stop saying that. Its an excuse. One that if we intend to become a multi-planet species we must change.
The history of space flight is short, roughly ~ 70 years at the time of this writing and in that time we have had many failures. These repeated failures have instilled the modality that space is hard.
